thread.title: BRIEF-Industrial & Infrastructure Fund Investment to buy interest in properties for totalling 6.79 bln yen

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Industrial & Infrastructure Fund Investment to buy interest in properties for totalling 6.79 bln yen

organizations.name: reuters) - industrial & infrastructure fund investment corp

text:
Jan 10 (Reuters) - Industrial & Infrastructure Fund Investment Corp
* Says it will buy Fukuoka-based property for 1.14 billion yen in total, on March 14
* Says it will buy 40 percent interest in Fukuoka-based property for 2.06 billion yen in total, on Feb. 1
* Says it will buy 40 percent interest in Fukuoka-based property for 3.59 billion yen in total, on Feb. 1
Source text in Japanese: goo.gl/fmYRfA
